4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring cybersecurity specialists with no prior knowledge. The program spans 16 weeks and includes three live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 16 students. Participants learn to secure Windows, Linux, networking, and server administration environments, while mastering cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The curriculum covers risk management using data loss prevention strategies and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop